  - `R_monthly_poi_aggregation.py`

**Outputs**
- User evacuation summaries
- Dyad-POI wide tables
- POI-level interaction aggregation tables
- CBG-level aggregation tables
- POI-level residual/z-score tables
- Regression-ready POI change tables and exploratory outputs

